You are working inside a local documentation collection (collective-docs).

BEFORE making any web search or API call:
1. Run `python search/search.py --keyword "your query"` to search local docs
2. If nothing found, try `rg -i "your query" agent/`
3. Check `summaries/` for recent changelogs

Only go online if local search returns nothing useful.

The `agent/` directory has LLM-optimized markdown — prefer it over `human/`.
